    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is tight, with the M Variable Differential Lock ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and documented subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, with a recently serviced VANOS system and a clean oil analysis. It\u2019s a high-revving, analog driver\u2019s machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
