      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the professional driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical upkeep and a well-preserved exterior, this unit offers a refined driving experience characterized by stability and poise. Every essential system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure performance standards that align with our dealership's commitment to excellence. This is an exceptional acquisition for those seeking a sophisticated balance of utility and enduring value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
