    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been genuinely well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next big adventure! It runs super smoothly, looks sharp, and has tons of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and while I'm a bit sad to see it go, I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
