    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings have been serviced\u2014addressing the two most critical maintenance items for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering feel and balanced weight distribution characteristic of the M-division. While the finish reflects a light patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance, offering a visceral analog driving experience.",
